comments: Lillard (MIL) and Brunson (NYK) are moving toward one another as they each pursue the loose ball and incidental body contact occurs when they come together.
Replay review of the out of bounds call pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Lillard's (MIL) right hand touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Lillard (MIL) places his hands on Grimes' (NYK) hips as Grimes moves to set the screen and marginal contact occurs before Lillard disengages.
Hart (NYK) is extending slightly as he firms up over his left foot and he does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Randle (NYK) releases his off-arm away from Antetokounmpo's (MIL) front and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo's momentum continues to carry him further into the lane.
Robinson (NYK) brushes Lopez's (MIL) arm and the contact is marginal as he loses control of the ball on his own.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Lopez (MIL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his right arm toward Randle's (NYK) path and marginal contact occurs with Randle's front as he drives toward the free throw line.
Lillard (MIL) and Grimes (NYK) engage and disengage with one another in the corner.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in Grimes' (NYK) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Lillard's (MIL) left hand comes forward and slides off of Brunson's (NYK) side/back as marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Lillard (MIL) is drawn forward slightly on the pump fake toward Brunson (NYK) and marginal body contact occurs prior to the start of Brunson's upward shooting motion.
Lillard (MIL) legally contests Brunson's (NYK) jump shot attempt, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.

Lopez (MIL) establishes a wide screening position and continues to extend as he attempts to firm up over his left foot, initiating contact with Hart's (NYK) lower body and side that dislodges Hart from his defensive position.
Grimes (NYK) extends his left arm into Lillard's (MIL) back and initiates contact that alters Lillard's layup attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Randle (NYK) during the driving shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Crowder (MIL) and Brunson (NYK) engage and disengage with one another following the inbound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) turns with his left arm brought outward and marginal contact occurs with Randle's (NYK) side/front during the drive.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) slightly extends laterally prior to absorbing the marginal body contact that occurs with Randle (NYK) after Randle's gather.
Hart (NYK) initiates contact across Lopez's (MIL) left arm during the rebound.
Crowder (MIL) immediately slides his hand off of Hart's (NYK) midsection and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Lopez (MIL) initiates contact with Brunson's (NYK) back and head/neck area in the post.
Crowder (MIL) brushes Brunson's (NYK) left shoulder and marginal contact occurs after Brunson's gather.
Brunson (NYK) initiates contact across Lillard's (MIL) left arm in the backcourt.
Randle (NYK) and Lillard's (MIL) arms become tangled in the backcourt and marginal contact occurs before they separate.
